	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Fun with a Pencil by Andrew Loomis is a good foundational book. It focuses on shape which lends itself to a cartoony style.
<br />
<br />The Vilppu Drawing Manual is also a good book.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


